1949;;The Clay Pigeon;;American;;Richard Fleischer;;Barbara Hale, Bill Williams;;crime drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Clay_Pigeon;;Jim Fletcher (Williams), a former inmate in a Japanese prisoner-of-war camp, awakes from a coma at a naval hospital, only to be told he's been accused of murder. Fletcher is not quite certain of his guilt so he escapes from the hospital in search of his best friend, another ex-POW.